# Designer drops generated skin variants here per
# docs/skins/placeholder-generation.md, then runs tools/skins/upload.ps1
# (R1.2) to push them to R2.
#
# Folder layout (created by the designer, not by code):
#   {characterId}/{skinId}/v{n}/{thumb,avatar,portrait,banner}.png
#
# This .gitkeep keeps the parent dir tracked while the staging artifacts
# themselves stay outside git (they live in R2, not in the repo).
